    'legal.arbitration.exception.description':
      "Notwithstanding the parties' agreement to resolve all disputes through arbitration, we may seek injunctive relief, specific performance and other equitable relief against you to enforce these Terms of Use in the state or federal courts located in Miami-Dade County, Florida as provided in Section 7(F) below.",
    'legal.arbitration.optout.title': '30 Day Right to Opt Out',
